column5: This angel dropped down from heaven to visit northwest Ontario. Merry Christmas!
Sweet pic Steve.Great bunch of crappies.Is that your grandson.You and your family have a great Xmas and will see you shortly after.Weather forecast is looking very good.
Actually that is Collin's little girl, I won't won't let it slip you called her a boy! That picture was taken last winter
Got you.Hard to tell in all those clothes.I remember Colin coming over there.
Nice pic, Steve. Looks like a great start to dinner. Happy Holidays.
I had to do a little Christmas afternoon fishing today, caught enough for tomorrow's lunch and left the rest for another day.
